text:
do u have any idea how to change dynamically the texts and icons color of the statusbar? The color is default white but when I have a light colored toolbar I need dark texts and icons.

 &lt;style name="LightstatusBarStyle" parent=“AppTheme"&gt;
        &lt;item name="android:windowLightStatusBar"&gt;true&lt;/item&gt;
    &lt;/style&gt;

    &lt;style name="DarkstatusBarStyle" parent=“AppTheme"&gt;
        &lt;item name="android:windowLightStatusBar"&gt;false&lt;/item&gt;
    &lt;/style&gt;
